{"word":"G2005 - ἐπιτελέω - epiteléō - ep-ee-tel-eh'-o - Accomplish","slug":"G2005","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτελέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epiteléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-tel-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Accomplish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - epiteleo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ee-tel-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5055\">G5055</a>; to <i>fulfill further</i> (or <i>completely</i>), that is, <i>execute</i>; by implication to <i>terminate</i>, <i>undergo:</i> - accomplish, do, finish, (make) (perfect), perform (X -ance)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5052\">G5052</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056\">G5056</a>"}]}